schools.name: Lillion E Luehrs J High School

data.description: This AMAZING property has it all! Country living just minutes from the City. This gorgeous two story home has been well maintained and shows pride of ownership. Kitchen has stainless steel appliances surrounded by custom cabinets and walkin pantry with new flooring installed 7/23. Granite countertops throughout. 1/2 bath downstairs next to built in secretary desk. Formal dining with walk in closet(being used as an office). Large laundry room with more storage. Master bedroom is downstairs with an oversized bathroom, gorgeous-just installed garden tub with his/her separate closets and his/her shower installed 5/23. Custom wood stairs installed 7/23. Upstairs features 3 bedrooms with walk in closets. One bedroom has a bonus private 1/2 bath from the walk-in second closet. Outside features a covered patio overlooking the fire pit and 1 acre. Plenty of room for a pool/batting cage, garden, 4-H projects and horses! Don't miss the detached 3 car garage AND additional well house/garage.
